This directory contafor most simple text preprocessing code. It can be used with classical topic models, such as LDA.
The functionalities include:
    - Remove non-ascii characters/words                     (1)
    - Remove non-english texts                              (1)
    - Lemmatize words                                       (1)
    - Remove non-alphabetic characters/words                (1)
    - Remove stopwords                                      (1)
    - Remove words shorter than n1 characters               (1)
    - Remove words having document frequency less than n2   (2)
    - Remove words having total frequency less than n3      (2)
    - Remove documents shorter than n3                      (2)
    - Transform words into word indices                     (2)
